'''''Mary Mary''''' is an American [[reality television]] series that aired on [[WE tv]] from March 29, 2012, to November 2, 2017.<ref>{{cite press release|title=WE tv Launches a Brand-New Original Series - "Mary Mary" Premieres Thursday, March 29 at 10PM ET/PT|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/01/14/we-tv-launches-a-brand-new-original-series-mary-mary-premieres-thursday-march-29-at-10pm-et-pt-641513/20120114we03/|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=February 2, 2013|date=January 14, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Careers Thrive. Can the Duo Survive? WE tv's "Mary Mary" Returns for Season 2 on Thursday, December 6 at a Special Time 10PM ET/PT|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/10/24/careers-thrive-can-the-duo-survive-we-tvs-mary-mary-returns-for-season-2-on-thursday-december-6-at-a-special-time-10pm-et-pt-387001/20121024we01/|accessdate=December 7, 2012}}</ref> The series follows the daily lives of sisters and musicians, [[Mary Mary|Erica and Tina Campbell]], as they balance their households and careers.<ref>{{cite news|title=Mary Mary Debuts Reality Show On WEtv|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/30/mary-mary-debuts-reality-show_n_1391258.html|publisher=HuffPost Multicultural|accessdate=February 2, 2013|author=JONATHAN LANDRUM Jr.|date=March 30, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Weisman|first=Jon|title=WE TV renews 'Mary Mary': Unscripted series on singing pair set to come back in 2013|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-201205101400reedbusivarietynvr1118053783may10,0,3245565.story|publisher=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=February 2, 2013}}</ref>

