'''Sofia Wistam''', during a time ''Eriksson'', nee ''Eklöf'' (born 15 May 1966, [[Lidingö]], [[Stockholm County]], [[Sweden]]) is a [[Swedish people|Swedish]] television host on [[TV4 (Sweden)|TV4]] and [[TV3 (Sweden)|TV3]] and radio talk-show host.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/wendela/barn/article333720.ab |title=Sofia Wistam gravid &#124; Barn &#124; Wendela &#124; Aftonbladet |publisher=Aftonbladet.se |date=2012-04-23 |accessdate=2012-08-26}}</ref> She has also worked as a stylist for stars such as [[Carola Häggkvist|Carola]], [[Jerry Williams (singer)|Jerry Williams]] and [[Tommy Nilsson]]. In 2008, she was also a judge on the talent show ''[[Talang 2008|Sweden's Got Talent]]'', during this year she also hosted her own radio show on Rix FM.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rixfm.com/?specialcontent=programledare&programledareID=53 |title=RIXFM |publisher=RIXFM |date= |accessdate=2012-08-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001101550/http://www.rixfm.com/?specialcontent=programledare&programledareID=53 |archivedate=1 October 2011 |df= }}</ref>

During 2009, Wistam hosted the competition show ''[[Wipeout (2008 U.S. game show)|Wipeout]]'' on Swedish television.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/1.1341611/wipeout-med-sofia-wistam-lockar-tavlingssugna |title=Wipeout med Sofia Wistam lockar tävlingssugna &#124; Nöje &#124; Expressen Nöje &#124; Nöjesnyheter Musiknyheter Filmnyheter |publisher=Expressen.se |date=2008-09-24 |accessdate=2012-08-26}}</ref>

Wistam was a contestant in [[Let's Dance 2013]].

